.TH DCR-NEW 1 "2026-06-02" "dcr 0.7.0" "DCR Manual"
.SH NAME
dcr-new \- Create a new DCR project
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B dcr new \fI<name>\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates a new C/C++ project with the given name. The name may only
contain ASCII letters, digits, underscores and hyphens.
.SH EXAMPLE
.B dcr new my-project
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR dcr (1),
.BR dcr-init (1)
